f this approach on the main longitudinal\ncharacteristics of proton-induced air showers and compare the predictions of\nthe well known CORSIKA code using the QGSJET hadronic interaction model.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 15 Nov 2004 19:46:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-10"}
