 large number of intermediate-mass stars in the field of the system, while\nthe general LMC field is found to be responsible for the low-mass population,\nwith M < 2 M_solar, observed in both fields.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 16 Nov 2004 14:38:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 17 Jan 2005 13:39:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-10-13"}
